<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="IE=edge">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.0.2/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet" integrity="sha384-EVSTQN3/azprG1Anm3QDgpJLIm9Nao0Yz1ztcQTwFspd3yD65VohhpuuCOmLASjC" crossorigin="anonymous">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://use.fontawesome.com/releases/v5.15.4/css/all.css" integrity="sha384-DyZ88mC6Up2uqS4h/KRgHuoeGwBcD4Ng9SiP4dIRy0EXTlnuz47vAwmeGwVChigm" crossorigin="anonymous">
    <%- include("../style/cloudStyle.ejs") %> 
    <title>SignIn</title>
</head>

<body class="d-flex flex-column justify-content-center" style="height: 100vh;">
    <div class="row d-flex justify-content-center text-center" style="width: 100vw; max-height: 30rem;">
        <div class="col-12 col-lg-10">
            <h3>Welcome to HomeAssist cloud manager software</h3>
            <p>Now you are starting your cloud for the very first time. In form bellow you should create first cloud user with admin rights. Don't forget to select the checkbox "Is Admin ?". Write down your E-mail address and your password and then hit Sign Up button. We hope you enjoy using our cloud manager.</p>
            <form action="/firstSignIn" method="post" class="form-signin px-3 d-flex flex-column align-items-center">
                <i class="fab fa-soundcloud text-primary" style="font-size: 8rem;">
                    <i class="fas fa-user-plus fs-3 text-primary"></i>
                </i>
                <label for="inputEmail" class="sr-only">Email address</label>
                <input type="email" name="email" id="inputEmail" class="form-control mb-1 w-50" placeholder="Email address" required autofocus>
                <label for="inputPassword"  class="sr-only">Password</label>
                <input type="password" name="password" id="inputPassword" class="form-control w-50" placeholder="Password" required>
                <div class="d-flex mt-2">
                    <input class="form-check-input mx-3" type="checkbox" value="true" name="admin" id="flexCheckDefault">
                    <label class="form-check-label" for="flexCheckDefault">
                    Is Admin ?
                </label>
                </div>
                <button class="btn w-25 btn-primary btn-block mt-3" type="submit">Sign in</button>
                <p class="mt-5 mb-3 text-muted">&copy; 2022 - Now</p>
              </form>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
<style>
    #inputEmail {
        border-radius: 5px 5px 0px 0px;
    }

    #inputPassword {
        border-radius: 0px 0px 5px 5px;
    }
</style>
<script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.0.2/dist/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js" integrity="sha384-MrcW6ZMFYlzcLA8Nl+NtUVF0sA7MsXsP1UyJoMp4YLEuNSfAP+JcXn/tWtIaxVXM" crossorigin="anonymous">
</script>

</html>